{"tid":383624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾蟲大戰食環 3人當場瞓低","createTime":"2017-09-01T15:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T03:33:15.000Z","uid":90060,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91b38d1bd2571b6ce9bb098408c12447db326792","tid":383624,"uid":90060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:37:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/osCvwLPUfXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FosCvwLPUfXA&d=NL2wxML9PHmKuXjXFwwIKJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a296122a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/osCvwLPUfXA</a><br />\n<br />\n食環署指人員目擊一名男子亂拋煙蒂，於是上前執法，但對方拒絕合作。事件中共4名人員遇襲受傷送院<br />\n<br />\n傍晚6時許，多名身穿制服的食環署職員，在大圍港鐵站外執勤時報稱遇襲，共有4名人員受傷。其中一男一女食環職員與該名男子均倒地，警方接報到場調查後，列作普通襲擊，拘捕55歲姓池男子。<br />\n<br />\n食環署發言人晚上回覆表示，事發於今日下午約6時15分，兩名食環署小販事務隊人員在大圍火車站外執行職務期間，目擊一名男子亂拋煙蒂，遂上前採取執法行動。但該名男子拒絕出示身分證，並襲擊兩名人員，人員遂要求警方協助，期間該名男子並與兩名隨後到場增援的食環署人員發生推撞。其後警方到場，4名食環署人員被送院治療，涉事男子亦一併送院。案件交由警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57157999&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57157999%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170901&d=NL2wxML9PHmKuXjXFwwIKJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=467bed94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57157999%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170901&h=ea7d3f10\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57157999&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170901</a>"},{"pid":"fcde8b873f4328f48da422d670bb96b509aab686","tid":383624,"uid":7125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"食環真辛苦 每個對手都係葉問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2412592e89573d567e2abb5e2a2f76674cab3abb","tid":383624,"uid":6347,"li